rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0001
rows.name: Shin.. I don't know what to do now...

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0002
rows.name:
I never thought we'd be
discovered here.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0003
rows.name:
17 years went by, and no one
found us...

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0004
rows.name:
If he knows I'm Iiran state property,
then we need to take him out.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0005
rows.name:
If we don't stop him now, he'll set the
army on us.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0006
rows.name: You're right. We have no choice.

rows.label: campfev11_090_100_msg0007
rows.name: Let's go back to Feltley Village.
